Required packages:
------------------
* apache2
* apache2-mod_perl
* perl-HTML-Parser
* sqlite
* perl-DBI
* perl-DBD-SQLite

Setup
-----

enhance /etc/sysconfig/apache2 APACHE_MODULES with "perl"

copy <SVN>trunk/apache2/mod_perl-startup.pl /etc/apache2/
copy <SVN>trunk/apache2/conf.d/mod_perl.conf /etc/apache2/conf.d/

copy <SVN>trunk/www/perl-lib/* /srv/www/perl-lib/

Read the README in <SVN>trunk/db/ , create the database and copy it
to /srv/www/  (we are searching for a better place)

rcapache2 start

